HEADWORD: Executioner
<hw>Ex`e*cu"tion*er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<def>One who executes; an executer.</def> <rj><au>Bacon.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>One who puts to death in conformity to legal
warrant, as a hangman.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Executive</ent>⟦br⟧
